===Students===
* [[Aiden Gillespie (Earth-616)|Anachronism (Aiden)]] - A former chubby gamer who recently gained the body of an immortal Celtic warlord god.{{r|Avengers Arena Vol 1 2}}{{r|Avengers Arena Vol 1 6}}
* [[Katy & Timothy Bashir (Earth-616)|Apex (Katy Bashir)]] - Extremely intelligent and manipulative flyer{{r|Avengers Arena Vol 1 2}} and secret technopath.{{r|Avengers Arena Vol 1 9}} Currently dating Kid Briton.{{r|Avengers Arena Vol 1 2}} She was murdered by [[Rebecca Ryker (Earth-616)|Death Locket]].{{r|Avengers Arena Vol 1 18}}
* [[Cullen Bloodstone (Earth-616)|Bloodstone (Cullen Bloodstone)]] - The youngest member of the famous monster hunting family. Sullen, but extremely bright and observant.{{r|Avengers Arena Vol 1 2}}
* [[Roger Bochs Jr. (Earth-616)|Box (Roger Bochs Jr.)]] - Son of the famous [[Roger Bochs (Earth-616)|Roger Bochs]], scientist and engineer. Box operates in an exoskeleton-style construct based on his father's original design but modified to increase his speed and strength ten-fold. Roger Jr. suffers from the same congenital condition that robbed his father of his legs at birth.{{r|Infinity: The Hunt Vol 1 1}}
* [[Brian Braddock (Earth-13022)|Kid Briton (Brian Braddock)]] - An [[Earth-13022|alter universe]], teenage version on [[Captain Britain]].{{r|Avengers Arena Vol 1 5}} Sometimes he's a cocky twit. Currently dating Apex{{r|Avengers Arena Vol 1 2}} though "secretly" having an affair with Nara. He was beheaded by Aiden when he tried to attack Nara.{{r|Avengers Arena Vol 1 6}}
* [[Kid Copper (Robert) (Earth-616)|Kid Copper (Bobby)]] - a boy with an enchanted police helmet which helps him solve mysteries. {{r|All-New Marvel NOW! Point One Vol 1 1.NOW}}
* [[Loch (Earth-616)|Loch]] - Has tough, scaly skin and arms with nearly unlimited strength and flexibility. Loch can also swim rapidly and breathe underwater.{{r|Infinity: The Hunt Vol 1 1}}
* [[Melanie Kapoor (Earth-61112)|Magic Boots Mel (Melanie Kapoor)]] - Young girl equipped with a pair of magical soccer shoes endowing her with the ability to kick and aim over great distances and making her invincible while dribbling.{{r|Avengers Assemble Vol 2 #15AU}}
* [[Nara (Earth-616)|Nara]] - An [[Atlantean]] orphan and exile with a violent temper and abandonment issues.{{r|Avengers Arena Vol 1 2}}{{r|Avengers Arena Vol 1 15}} "Secretly" having an affair with Kid Briton.{{r|Avengers Arena Vol 1 6}} Sacrificed herself to prevent Aiden from killing his best friend, Cullen.{{r|Avengers Arena Vol 1 15}}
* At least 8-12 other unidentified students, possibly more.{{r|Avengers Arena Vol 1 6}}

